cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about single image super-resolution using deep learning, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a method to regularize deep structures with natural image priors, which is a technique commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves experiments and results, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
